### MedicalAgent API Tests
### Use REST Client extension (humao.rest-client) to execute these requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5200

### ============================================
### Health Check Endpoints
### ============================================

### Check if the API is alive
GET {{baseUrl}}/alive
Accept: application/json

###

### Check if the API is ready (includes MCP server health)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### Chat API Endpoints
### ============================================

### Get complete medical history for a patient
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "What is the complete medical history for patient 1?"
}

###

### Query specific patient medications
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "What medications is patient 2 currently taking?"
}

###

### Query patient conditions
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "What medical conditions does patient 1 have?"
}

###

### Query patient allergies
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Does patient 3 have any known allergies?"
}

###

### Query lab results with date range
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Show me patient 1's lab results from January 2024 to December 2024"
}

###

### Query recent visits
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "What were the recent medical visits for patient 2?"
}

###

### Ask without patient ID (should prompt for clarification)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "What is the patient's blood pressure?"
}
